content: Thanks for the tips! I'll definitely keep them in mind when I meet up with Alex. So, speaking of meeting new people, I've also been reconnecting with some old friends from high school. Last month, I met up with Christine, who's back in town after living abroad for a few years. We grabbed brunch and caught up on each other's lives. It was amazing to see how much she's grown and changed, and I'm glad we're still close despite the distance.
